code: @Override protected MediaType getContentType() {     return new MediaType("text", "event-stream", StandardCharsets.UTF_8). }
@Override public boolean checkSessionType(SockJsSession session) {     return session instanceof EventSourceStreamingSockJsSession. }

@Override public StreamingSockJsSession createSession(String sessionId, WebSocketHandler handler, Map<String, Object> attributes) {     return new EventSourceStreamingSockJsSession(sessionId, getServiceConfig(), handler, attributes). }
@Override protected SockJsFrameFormat getFrameFormat(ServerHttpRequest request) {     return new DefaultSockJsFrameFormat("data: %s\r\n\r\n"). }
@Override protected byte[] getPrelude(ServerHttpRequest request) {     return new byte[] { '\r', '\n' }. }
